=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_GlitchBPF_ex1 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark clean sound, with saw_like oscillator character around 50 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and compressed envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally sparse.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: compressed
  envelope_flatness: dynamic
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: clean
  spectral_complexity_mean: sparse
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 50.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: -2.5220
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9830
  pitch_clarity: 30.7265
  inharmonicity: 0.1987
  type: saw_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -7.6414
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

